Package org.dalesbred.instantiation

Conversion of database results to classes and vice versa.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    InstantiationListener
    A listener which is notified whenever an Instantiator has created a new object.
    Instantiator<T>
    Factory for producing objects from given arguments.
    InstantiatorRegistry
    Provides access to the publicly available configuration interface of DefaultInstantiatorRegistry.
    TypeConversionRegistry
    Registry containing the TypeConversions used when converting database values to objects and vice versa.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultInstantiatorRegistry
    Provides Instantiators for classes.
    InstantiatorArguments
    Contains the arguments of instantiator as well their names and types.
    NamedTypeList
    Represents a named list of types, e.g.
    NamedTypeList.Builder
    Builder for NamedTypeLists.
    TypeConversion<S,T>
    A conversion from S into T.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InstantiationException
    Exception thrown when there is a problem with instantiation or coercion.
